body: "Items with release field matching a known git tag bucket to that section; items without release field fall back to timestamp window. Empty release windows are omitted unless includeEmpty is set. The generator runs release-field bucketing first, then timestamp filtering for remaining items, guaranteeing each item appears in exactly one section."
